{"tid":1923133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有中學生派口罩 但唔夠人推搞到無人知 想幫學生都幫唔到","createTime":"2020-03-13T02:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T08:35:25.000Z","uid":153864,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cf36a7be4afece215010a7e293e75608d57187","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/13/095650_7261ffe9c0b0193b5b1b0e0b1fd10272.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F13%2F095650_7261ffe9c0b0193b5b1b0e0b1fd10272.png&h=00f7c18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B9ooOSLHQtQ/?igshid=f0e9vastm9he\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB9ooOSLHQtQ%2F%3Figshid%3Df0e9vastm9he&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=014c1c52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB9ooOSLHQtQ%2F%3Figshid%3Df0e9vastm9he&h=b32fc942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B9ooOSLHQtQ/?igshid=f0e9vastm9he</a><br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎在香港全面爆發，口罩亦成走在街上的必需品，所見社區亦甚少口罩派發學生。<br />\n許多有需要的學生亦缺乏口罩，卻沒有財力捱市面貴價口罩。<br />\n我們現藉有心人的捐獻，作為橋樑幫助有需要的中學生。<br />\n<br />\n我們首階段計劃覆蓋全港中學生，只要你需要，憑有效中學學生證便能從我們手上領取口罩。<br />\n<br />\n由於資金入不敷支，次階段計劃還在籌備當中。假如你不是學生，你又希望可以捐助口罩/資金，歡迎dm我們。<br />\n<br />\n政府不救，學生自救！ （備注：每位同學只限申請一次，一位同學可以領取7個口罩）<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n佢地只係一班好有心嘅中學生<br />\n係想幫下學生 就算要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n墊錢<br />\n</span></span>買口罩都想買定數量嘅口罩派比學生 但都唔夠人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢地資金又唔夠 但佢地真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好有心做</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c8784208ee3d70d7fcf45d07b447a04bc0f9c1","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"3e185e5201456c845a5bafa066e06f75f902b0ed","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"da9a744407b855e67567829dcdfacc446ab6e7de","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cbaed2233cfbf0b20d86b9999d8dcd8ed9a80bf1","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"3e8cb59dd7bd3ddff996c28d9cad2525a104fa18","tid":1923133,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0008e37eb70ddff8a5c807bd8d4f4079c404244","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"b76b0dfdf80c705352f09cf09d60feb2a0480d1f","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"7e50920449c85e14ffaabe61b1f790e9e1582450","tid":1923133,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"b602f8639fa73d61178b91d42a5a336f4f169e91","tid":1923133,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b0faa774ac02e055df710a147e341c7a8c65137","tid":1923133,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f